HEADWORD: Matteuccia
<hw>Matteuccia</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A small genus sometimes
included in genus <gen>Onoclea</gen>; in some classifications both
genera are placed in <gen>Polypodiaceae</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Matteuccia</gen>, Pteretis, genus
<gen>Pteretis</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

